        <h2 class="node__title">
            <a href="/article/social-partners-local-and-regional-governments-joint-declaration-covid19-and-its" rel="bookmark"><span property="dc:title">Social Partners in Local and Regional Governments joint declaration on COVID19 and its consequences</span>
</a>
        </h2>
      <span property="dc:title" content="Social Partners in Local and Regional Governments joint declaration on COVID19 and its consequences" class="hidden"></span>
  <span property="sioc:num_replies" datatype="xsd:integer" class="hidden"></span>

    <p class="article-country">
        
    </p>
            <a href="/article/social-partners-local-and-regional-governments-joint-declaration-covid19-and-its" class="article--resume" rel="bookmark">
                <div property="content:encoded" class="field field--body body field--text-with-summary field--hidden">
        <div class="field-items">
                            <div><p>The COVID-19 pandemic is a health crisis. However, the tough but needed measures to contain the virus have led to an economic crisis and without the appropriate measures we risk exacerbating the emerging social crisis</p>
</div>
                    </div>
    </div>

        </a>
                            <aside class="article__aside">
              
                <div class="field--policies">
                  <div class="field-item">
